@startuml
!theme plain
title 10. Coherence Write Policy
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "KV mutation" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Durability classifier" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Write-around/back/through" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "OpenZFS sync path" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Ack policy" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : state update
N2 --> N3 : KV-D class
N3 --> N4 : write mode
N4 --> N5 : durable commit

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
